{"tid":2189781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（戰狼本色）太極宗師30秒被KO　弟子出戰一樣被打爆","createTime":"2020-09-05T06:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T07:40:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"03c71f19d55e54d4c89e0978e57065ed77242a71","tid":2189781,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:28:44.000Z","msg":"中國格鬥界似乎出現一群「嘴砲系統」，自稱是「渾元形意太極拳掌門人」的68歲馬保國，自己被業餘選手30秒KO大敗後，馬保國弟子葉廷也在3日的一場格鬥賽中，被搏擊網紅阿虎完全打爆，在2回合比賽中，葉廷慘遭阿虎3次擊倒...<br />\n<br />\n不少網友也調侃葉廷與馬保國，說兩人「有其師必有其徒」，稱葉廷在賽前放話，要對手去買拐杖，「簡直跟他師父一樣，吹最大的牛，挨最毒的打！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200905/4IJSYUPIGFCFDHOKUF5U6IXO3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200905%2F4IJSYUPIGFCFDHOKUF5U6IXO3E%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs40YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=db8bf848\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200905%2F4IJSYUPIGFCFDHOKUF5U6IXO3E%2F&h=235d3469\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200905/4IJSYUPIGFCFDHOKUF5U6IXO3E/</a>"},{"pid":"68d4545153b4309df8b265578d123c4e9f6b9253","tid":2189781,"uid":29093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:32:20.000Z","msg":"都係太極張三豐啲劇集同電影累事 <br />\n<br />\n搞班班廢老以為自己舉世無雙咁款"},{"pid":"d9561d2509a8dac6275819c9cb1fc4c5aec98914","tid":2189781,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68d4545153b4309df8b265578d123c4e9f6b9253","tid":2189781,"uid":29093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:32:20.000Z","msg":"都係太極張三豐啲劇集同電影累事 <br />\n<br />\n搞班班廢老以為自己舉世無雙咁款"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"以前無乜娛樂，唯有吹到自己可以一掌打死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba12311fcc9bfd74ac968668bc65f87482dad83","tid":2189781,"uid":22362,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-